(322, 1, '2015-05-25 04:31:35', '2015-05-25 04:31:35', '\r\n<div class="container contact-feature">\r\n<p class="feature-center">Call us for an obligation free quote!(07) 3823 1044</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="container home-content feature-center">\r\n<h1 class="feature-center page-heading">Testimonials</h1>\r\n\r\n <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"My wife and I would like to express our sincere thanks for the work you undertook in making our kitchen an outstanding feature in our new home. From the initial consultation involving a combined input of ideas to your several pre-inspections of the building through to the fabrication of the kitchen; you and your team demonstrated the level of professionalism and eye for detail that has become a rarity these days. A special thanks to the crew who took such care in the packing of the components and their delivery to site as well as to Mick who did such a thorough job assembling and installing on site. Every gap is perfect, everything works the way it should. The kitchen is a delight to work in and it makes us happy every day."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- Kevin and Julie Gillam</small>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"We have found Greg and his staff to be approachable and friendly and ready to offer assistance if necessary. I would have no hesitation in recommending this company to any future client wishing to undertake business with him."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- Moreton Bay Boys'' College</small>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"The thing that impressed us most about Greg was his experience, quietly pointing out little things on our wish list that could save us money, improve the overall look of the project and improve long term things...  His meticulous attention to detail overwhelmed us from the start."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- Chris and Maree Shaw</small>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"I came across GJ Cabinets through a former work colleague who was happy with the work done for him by GJ Cabinets. Greg, the proprietor of GJ Cabinets, personally came and measured for our kitchen cabinets. We are very happy with the finished product as he was able to cater for our needs which included our custom designed cabinets and bench tops. Greg was very helpful and accommodating that he was able to provide the non-standard items the we wanted in our kitchen. As GJ Cabinets makes the cabinets in Brisbane, any unforeseen site problems could be rectified within a short time. The tradesmen who carried out the sub-contract work for GJ Cabinets were very professional in their work. I have since engaged some of these tradesmen to do work for me. Since completing the kitchen in April 2013, I subsequently engaged GJ Cabinets to make and install vanity cabinets for two bathrooms, and we are very happy with the work also."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- Gordon Lee</small>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"Greg and his team and GJ Cabinets put my vision into reality!! From beginning to end, Greg was nothing but professional, courteous and extremely patient. GJ Cabinets did everything for me, from design and colour selections to organising all my kitchen appliances, sorted all the trades (plumber, electrician, tiler, plasterer) and even arranged the new floor coverings. Greg''s attention to detail and high expectations for quality, from his team from manufacturing to installation are a credit to him and his business. The whole process was as promised, from the first check measure to the day of installation, it ran like clockwork. I would have no hesitation to use Greg and his business again, and would highly recommend him to anyone."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- J. Salmon</small>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"I love my new kitchen, not only for its sleek lines and smooth finish, but for its logic. Everything has a place and the place is exactly where it out to be. ...Greg creates magic every day and probably doesn''t even realise he is turning time spent in the kitchen into hours of pleasure and ease."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- John and Linda Muller</small>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n         <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"Greg is extremely calm and very customer-focused. He listens deeply to client ideas and marries these with his practical experience and advice. ...GJ Cabinets are equally comfortable taking the lead and suggesting ''what works'' for most households."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- Brian and Jenny</small>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"Having used you years ago to do our bathroom and laundry reno we didn''t even bother to shop around, we knew who we would use for our kitchen. Your work is faultless."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- Mike and Robyn</small>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"All staff of GJ Cabinets were efficient, showed attention to detail, worked as a team and turned up when they said they would."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- Daniel and Maria Gordon</small>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class="col-md-12 testimonial-box">\r\n          <p>"This is the third kitchen you have now done for us over the past 10 years and we would not use anyone else."</p>\r\n          <p><small>- Gordon and Jean</small>\r\n        </div>                  \r\n  </div>\r\n<div class="container content-cap"></div>', 'Testimonials', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '171-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-25 04:31:35', '2015-05-25 04:31:35', '', 171, 'http://technople.in/gjcabinets/2015/05/25/171-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
