(349, 1, '2015-05-25 10:44:54', '2015-05-25 10:44:54', '     \r\n<div class="contact-feature">\r\n<p class="feature-center">Call us for an obligation free quote!(07) 3823 1044</p>\r\n</div>\r\n      <div class="home-content feature-center">\r\n        \r\n      <h1 class="feature-center page-heading">Cabinetmaking with pride.</h1>\r\n      \r\n      <p>GJ Cabinets is a Redlands-based cabinet making business that has been providing outstanding service to the Bayside region for over 10 years. Greg Calvert and his team have over 25 years of experience and can create custom-made cabinets and furniture calling on their personal wealth of industry knowledge. GJ Cabinets is renowned for their efficiency, attention to detail and practical advice for what best suits your needs. Working with a wide breadth of experience, Greg and his team can create spectacular kitchens, laundries, vanities, bars, home offices, media cabinets and more. They are fully licensed through the QBSA and also a member of the HIA (Housing industry Australia), bringing national standards to every job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nationally recognised, GJ Cabinets prides itself on client relations and ensuring a very personable experience every time. This is exemplified by Greg Calvert''s love of client satisfaction. Greg enjoys talking and listening to a client''s ideas and then builds on these to create a product that perfectly fits for your home or business. Greg and the team take pride in knowing they have left their customers happy with their product, something many of his competitors could not swear to. You are in safe hands with GJ Cabinets, one of the leading cabinet makers in the all of South-East Queensland. <i class="icon-bt-id-card"></i><i class="icon-bt-gear"></i></p>\r\n\r\n<p>But don''t take our word for it, read our client testimonials and be assured that GJ Cabinets puts your needs as first priority.</p>\r\n\r\n<a class="btn btn-primary margin" href="#" role="button">Why Choose Us?</a>\r\n\r\n<div cl